# Force LF line endings on shell scripts and Python so they run cleanly on
# macOS / Linux even if the working tree was last touched on Windows with
# core.autocrlf=true. Without this, scripts checked out on macOS contain
# CRLF and bash heredocs / shebangs break in non-obvious ways.
*.sh    text eol=lf
*.py    text eol=lf
*.yml   text eol=lf
*.yaml  text eol=lf
